{
  "texts": [
    "However, the COCO dataset still has some limitations that dramatically affect some object detection.",
    "Among these limitations:1.",
    "The limit of object categories contained only 80 object categories.",
    "This number represents very limited compared with countless other categories in the real world. 2.",
    "Like any other large-scale dataset, COCO is vulnerable to annotation errors."
  ]
}